I18N.en.layerExplain=[['Strategic · Temporistics','This level is not a “person type”; it is a hypothesis about how someone builds time, meaning and direction.','Example: two people may communicate well but see life pace, development and the future differently.'],['Operational · Action-and-decision map','This level shows how a person breaks down a task, assembles a solution and distributes effort.','Example: two people may want the same outcome but decide, push, support or argue differently.'],['Tactical · Socionics','This level shows how a person selects signals, links facts and builds a model of the situation.','Example: two people may want the same thing but repeatedly read context and intentions differently.']];

